metadata.name: 1984 - YOU ARE BEING WATCHED
metadata.description:
An artistic interpretation of the dystopian social science fiction novel by George Orwell, titled "1984".

The highly relevant themes of totalitarianism, mass surveillance, and repressive regimentation are expressed throughout.

The piece took 4 years to complete. Initially thought to be finished on 4/2016, additional work on 5/2018, and finally completed in 2/2020. 

Extremely detailed, filled with hidden characters, and will have you staring for hours.

1984 - YOU ARE BEING WATCHED
by
RabidArtWork
